Type: Package
Package: ellipsoidgaussian
Title: The ellipsoid-Gaussian model
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Hanyu Song
Maintainer: Hanyu Song <songhanyu1211@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides Bayesian estimation of the
    ellipsoid-Gaussian model, introduced by
    \insertCite{song2022curved}{ellipsoidgaussian}.  The
    ellipsoid-Gaussian distribution can be used to model data distributed
    around a hyper-ellipsoid.  It is induced when we use a Gaussian linear
    factor model with latent variables following a von Mises-Fisher
    distribution and have the latent variables integrated out. Options for
    generating samples from the posterior predictive distribution, and
    plotting results are also provided.
